| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2755 — Recovery Inhibition (killsec)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 8e9e3dce-2833-51ed-9c11-74cea1d0d69a"
